'''''The Nightingale's Prayer''''' ni film yo mu misiri yakozwe muri 1959 iyoborwa na Henry Barakat kandi ishingiye kuri novel y'umwanditsi ukomeye Taha Hussein . Irimo Faten Hamama na Ahmed Mazhar<ref>https://www.madamasr.com/en/2014/08/23/feature/culture/egypts-cinematic-gems-the-nightingales-prayer/</ref><ref>https://www.madamasr.com/en/2014/08/23/feature/culture/egypts-cinematic-gems-the-nightingales-prayer/</ref> <ref>https://www.theculturist.com/home/for-the-love-of-film-noir-a-nightingales-prayer.html</ref>.

Mu 1996, mugihe k'imyaka 100 ya Sinema yo muri Egiputa, iyi film yatoranijwe murimwe mu mafilime 150 meza yo muri Egiputa<ref>https://trakt.tv/movies/the-nightingale-s-prayer-1959</ref>. Yakiriye igihembo cyishimiwe n’ishuri rikuru ry’imashusho y’ubuhanzi n’ubumenyi kandi yatoranijwe  muri Filime nziza y’ururimi rw’amahanga mu bihembo bya 32 bya Academy, ariko ntiyemerwa nk'umukandida.<ref>https://trakt.tv/movies/the-nightingale-s-prayer-1959</ref> <ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the-nightingales-prayer</ref> Yinjiye kandi mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya 10 rya Berlin<ref>https://b.worldmisc.com/read/the-nightingale-s-prayer</ref> . 

